    <div id="nyt_about_blog-3" class="module nocontent widget_nyt_about_blog"><h4 class="moduleHeader">About</h4><div class="entry">
<p class="summary">This report on India from the journalists of <a href="http://www.nytimes.com/" title="The New York Times - Breaking News, World News & Multimedia">The New York Times</a> and a pool of talented writers in India and beyond provides unbiased, authoritative reporting on the country and its place in the world. <a href="http://india.blogs.nytimes.com/" title="India › Log In">India Ink</a> also strives to be a virtual meeting point for discussion of this complex, fast-changing democracy – its politics, economy, culture and everyday life.</p>
